'''Liyo Talstai''' adawaiz '''Leo Tolstoy''', ar Kount '''Lev Nikolayevich Tolstoy''' (9 Septemba 1828 - 20 Novemba 1910) a weh wah [[Rosha|Roshan]] raita we nof piipl kansida fi bi wan a di gudis navlis fi aal taim. Ih maastapiisdem ingkluud ''[[Waar ah Piis]]'' (War and Peace) ah ''[[Ana Kareniina]]'' (Anna Karenina).

